high_descs: Turn left, move forward, turn right at the sink.
Pick up the spoon in the sink.
Turn right, bring the spoon to the wall, turn left to face the bowl on the counter.
Put the spoon in the bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl with spoon on the counter.
Turn left, bring the bowl down to the sink on the to your right.
Put the bowl with spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it, in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and head forward, then hang right to walk to the kitchen sink.
Pick up a spoon that is on the floor.
Turn right and head to the wall, then turn left to face the kitchen counter.
Place the spoon upright in the blue bowl in back of the counter.
Pick up the blue bowl with the spoon in it.
Turn left and walk back to the kitchen sink.
Place the blue bowl in the sink  to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Take a spoon and place in a blue bowl then place the bowl in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink.
Pick up the spoon from the sink.
Turn right and go all the way to the wall then turn left toward the counter.
Put the spoon in the bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon.
Turn left and go to the sink and turn right towards it.
Place the bowl in the middle of sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl into the sink.
